.TH wrp2project 1 "February 2026" "arma-tools" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
wrp2project \- generate a Terrain Builder project from a WRP file
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wrp2project
.RI [ flags ]
.I input.wrp
.RI [ output_dir ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wrp2project
creates a project directory with terrain config, road data, layers, object imports, and TV4 project files.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI "--name " s
Override terrain name.
.TP
.BI "-offset-x " n
X coordinate offset (default 200000).
.TP
.BI "-offset-z " n
Z coordinate offset (default 0).
.TP
.BI "--prefix " s
Layer name prefix.
.TP
.BI "--roads " f
Road type mapping TSV.
.TP
.BI "--roads-shp " f
Import roads from SHP.
.TP
.BI "--config " f
Import metadata from derapified config.cpp.
.TP
.BI "--drive " d
Drive root for P3D paths.
.TP
.BI "--db " f
Use a3db database for model bounding boxes.
.TP
.BI "--split " n
Max objects per import file.
.TP
.BI "--style " f
JSON style map for TML output.
.TP
.BI "--hm-scale " n
Heightmap upscale factor (1,2,4,8,16).
.TP
.B
--extract-models
Extract models and textures to drive.
.TP
.B
--pretty
Pretty-print JSON output.
.TP
.BR -h , " --help"
Show help.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wrp_info (1),
.BR wrp_dump (1),
.BR a3db (1)
